'Yan majalisa a Wales sun damu da cewa za a yi musu kallon jarumai
Wasu 'yan majalisa a Wales sun yi fushi da shawarar da aka yi na maye gurbin lakabi da MWP (Member of the Welsh Parliament).
Wannan shawara ta samo asali ne daga wani shiri na sauya sunan majalisa, wanda zai zama majalisar dokokin Wales.
A fagen siyasa, wasu 'yan majalisa suna ganin cewa za a iya yi wa wannan ba'a.
Wani ɗan majalisar da ya fito daga jam'iyyar Labour ya ce ƙungiyarsa na damuwa da cewa kalmar nan  tana da ma'ana da Twp da Pwp .
Ga masu karatu da ba 'yan Wales ba: a yaren Welsh, twp yana nufin wawa, kuma pwp yana nufin kura.
Wani daga cikin mambobinta ya ce jam'iyyar Plaid Cymru (Welsh Party) ba ta gamsu ba kuma ta ba da wasu shawarwari.
Jam'iyyar Conservative ta ce tana shirye ta sauya sunan, amma ta ce tsakanin MWP da Muppet, ta yi nisa.
A wannan yanayin, a yaren Welsh, ana furta harafin w kamar yadda ake furta harafin u a yaren Turanci na yankin Yorkshire.
Kwamitin Majalisar, wanda ke shirin shirya dokar da za ta sauya sunan, ya ce 'ƙudurin ƙarshe game da nadin mambobin Majalisar ya rage ga mambobin majalisar'.
Dokar Gwamnatin Wales ta 2017 ta ba wa majalisar dokokin Wales ikon canza sunan ta.
A watan Yuni, Hukumar ta wallafa sakamakon wani taron jama'a kan shawarar da ta yi na kiran majalisar a matsayin majalisar Wales, kuma an samu goyon baya sosai.
A kan batun sunan 'yan majalisa, Hukumar ta fi son 'yan majalisa na Wales (WMP); duk da haka, yawancin mutanen Wales sun fi son MWP.
A bayyane yake cewa 'yan majalisa suna da wasu shawarwari, amma kokarin cimma yarjejeniya na iya zama babban ciwon kai ga Elin Jones, shugaban majalisa, wanda ake sa ran gabatar da kudurin sauya sunan a makonni masu zuwa.
Dokar ta gyara za ta hada da wasu canje-canje ga yadda majalisa ke aiki, musamman dokokin da suka shafi cire 'yan majalisa da kuma tsarin kwamitocin.
'Yan majalisa za su yanke shawara ta karshe kan batun sunan a lokacin da ake muhawara kan kudirin.
