Hukumar Kula da Yanayi ta Kasa ta riga ta ba da gargadin ambaliyar ruwa don Litinin da Talata a yammacin Arizona, kudu da gabashin Nevada, kudu maso gabashin California da Utah, gami da biranen Phoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas da Salt Lake City.
