Taron yakin neman zaben Trump a West Virginia (Yutube)
Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara taron yakin neman zabe a Wheeling, West Virginia, a daren yau.
An shirya wasu wuraren da za a kai ziyara, musamman jihohi kamar Tennessee da Mississippi inda shugaban kasa ya shahara.
Da yake an dage zaben tabbatar da gurbin da ake da shi a Kotun Koli, Trump na neman samun goyon baya a zaben da za a yi a tsakiyar wa'adin da ke tafe da kuma hana 'yan Republican rasa iko a majalisar dokoki a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump a West Virginia zai gudana yau da dare kuma ta yaya zan iya kallon sa a yanar gizo?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia da karfe 7 na dare (lokacin Gabas) a ranar Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon bidiyon a ƙasa, a kan YouTube.
Ana sa ran Trump zai tattauna batun sauraron karar da aka yi wa dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ake zargi da cin zarafin mata, a wannan makon.
Amma babban abin da taron ya kunsa shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican su samu rinjaye a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
A cewar Reuters, shugaban na Amurka ya bayyana a yakin neman zabensa cewa taron biyar na nufin karfafawa masu sa kai da magoya baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da fadada rinjaye da suke da su a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai.
 Kula da majalisar wakilai wani muhimmin bangare ne na shirinsa wanda shugaban zai ziyarci jihohi da yawa kamar yadda zai yiwu a farkon wannan yakin neman zabe, wani mai magana da yawun kungiyar Trump, wanda ya ki a bayyana sunansa, ya fadawa Reuters.
A cewar jaridar West Virginia Metro News, taron na yau da dare da aka shirya a gidan wasan Wesbanco Arena da ke Wheeling, zai iya tara magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania, kuma zai iya jawo hankalin kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh.
A ranar Asabar, wannan ita ce ziyarar Trump ta biyu a cikin wata guda zuwa jihar West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe a 2016 da kashi sama da 40.
Trump yana kokarin taimakawa Patrick Morrisey, dan takarar majalisar dattijai na jam'iyyar Republican a jihar West Virginia, wanda ke kan gaba a zaben.
 Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrisey cewa shugaban ya zo ya sake gwada shi a zaben, in ji Simon Haeder, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
