Bayan sun doke Woods da Patrick Reed a wasan hudu, sai suka doke dan wasan Amurka Bryson Dechambeau da Woods da ya gaji da wasan da suka yi da biyar da hudu.
Woods, wanda ya yi rashin lafiya a wasannin biyu da aka buga a ranar Asabar, ya yi wasa a wasu lokatai, amma yanzu ya yi rashin nasara a wasanni 19 cikin 29 da ya buga a wasanni hudu da hudu, kuma bakwai a jere.
Justin Rose, wanda ya huta sosai don wasan kwallon kafa na safe, ya yi aiki tare da Henrik Stenson a wasan kwallon kafa, inda ya ci nasara da Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepka, lamba ɗaya da uku a duniya.
Ƙasar Turai ta sha wahala a lokacin da aka yi gasar a birnin Paris, a lokacin da ake sanyi amma babu wata matsala.
Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas, 'yan wasan da suka yi nasara sau uku a gasar, sun kafa misali ga 'yan wasan Amurkawa ta hanyar zura kwallaye biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun sami nasarar da suka cancanci 2-1 a kan Mutanen Espanya Jon Rahm da Ian Poulter a cikin wasan kwallon kafa guda hudu kuma sun sake doke Poulter da Rory McIlroy 4-3 a cikin wasan kwallon kafa, waɗanda suka rasa ramukan farko biyu.
Sau biyu ne kawai a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup da wata kungiya ta sake dawowa daga tazarar maki hudu a wasan guda, duk da cewa tawagar Furyk, wacce ke rike da kambin, ta yi wasa ne kawai don riƙe kyautar.
