Yawancin waɗanda suka kamu da cutar sun kamu da cutar ta wajen jima'i, kuma wannan sabon abu ne.
A tarihi, cutar ta yadu da sauri a wasu sassan ƙasar ta hanyar ƙarin jini da ke da cutar.
Amma, adadin mutanen da ke kamuwa da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan babu, in ji hukumomin kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin a wani taro da aka yi a lardin Yunnan.
Amma, a kowace shekara, adadin mutanen da ke da cutar kanjamau a ƙasar Sin ya ƙaru da mutane 100,000.
A cikin al'ummar LGBT na kasar Sin, yaduwar cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce.
An dakatar da nuna luwadi a kasar Sin a shekarar 1997, amma nuna bambanci ga 'yan luwadi ya zama ruwan dare gama gari.
Domin halin da ake da shi a ƙasar, wasu bincike sun nuna cewa maza da yawa da suke yin luwadi suna aure.
Mutane da yawa suna kamuwa da cutar ta wajen yin jima'i da ba su da kariya.
A ƙoƙarin da gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi na magance wannan matsalar, ta yi alkawarin cewa za a samu maganin cutar HIV ga dukan mutane tun shekara ta 2003.
