A lokacin da aka buga wannan littafin, akwai abubuwa biyu da suka sa mutane farin ciki.
Na ji daɗin yadda Johnny English ya zo kusa da wani jirgin sama mai saukar ungulu da yake saka mayafin dā kuma da shigewar iska da ke kan makamai.
An nuna Atkinson don wasan kwaikwayo na jiki, ko da yake wasan kwaikwayo bai isa ba kuma ba shi da mahimmanci, musamman a lokacin da manyan lasisi kamar 007 da Mission Impossible suka yi aiki da kansu tare da wasan kwaikwayo.
Abin dariya yana da kyau ga yara fiye da manya, kuma a gare ni, Johnny English ba shi da basira da kuma hankali fiye da Atkinson a cikin fim din Bean.
Abin da ke faruwa a yanzu shi ne cewa ƙasar Biritaniya tana da matsaloli masu tsanani.
Wani dan leken asiri ya kutsa cikin babbar hanyar yanar gizo ta leken asirin Burtaniya, ya bayyana ainihin duk jami'an Burtaniya a fagen, abin takaici ga jami'an da ke aiki - rawar da Kevin Eldon ba ta da girma.
Wannan shi ne abin da ya sa aka yi wa Firaminista da ke da girman kai da kuma rashin amincewa da siyasa, wanda ke fuskantar matsalar tattalin arziki, ba da daɗewa ba: Emma Thompson ta yi iya ƙoƙarinta wajen yin fim ɗin da ya yi kama da na Theresa May, amma ba a sami wani abu mai kyau a cikin rubutun ba.
Masu ba ta shawara a fannin leken asiri sun gaya mata cewa tun da yake an yi wa kowane ɗan leken asiri barazana, za ta bukaci ta fitar da wani daga cikin waɗanda ta yi ritaya da su.
Wannan yana nufin cewa dole ne a damu da Johnny English kansa, wanda yanzu yake aiki a wata makarantar da ke da kyau a matsayin malamin makaranta, amma yana ba da darussan sirri game da yadda za a zama wakili na sirri: wasu manyan farfaganda a nan, saboda Turanci yana ba da makarantar leken asiri a cikin hanyar Rock Academy.
An dawo da Turanci zuwa Whitehall don taron gaggawa na gaggawa kuma ya sami Bough, tsohon abokin aikinsa, wanda Ben Miller ya sake kafa masa sansani.
Bough yanzu ya yi aure, yana da alaka da kwamandan jirgin ruwa, wani wasan hockey mai ban sha'awa wanda Vicki Pepperdine ya yi amfani da shi.
Don haka, Batman da Robin, waɗanda suka haifar da babbar matsala ga sabis na sirrin Mai Girma, sun koma aiki kuma sun haɗu da Olga Kurylenko, kyakkyawar mace mai ban mamaki Ophelia Bulletova.
A lokacin, Firaministan ya faɗa cikin hannun wani mai fasaha mai kuɗi da yawa wanda ya ce zai iya magance matsalolin kwamfuta na Biritaniya: Jason Volta, wanda Jake Lacy ya yi.
English da Bough sun soma yin ban dariya: suna yin kamar masu ba da abinci, sun ƙone wani gidan cin abinci na Faransa mai haske; sun haifar da hargitsi ta hanyar shiga cikin jirgin ruwa mai kyau na Volta; kuma English ya haifar da rashin tsari lokacin da yake ƙoƙarin, tare da kwalliyar gaskiya ta gaskiya, don sanin abin da ke cikin gidan Volta.
Dukkanin abubuwan da aka yi a wannan fim ɗin sun tabbata, amma duk da haka, akwai abubuwa da yawa da yara za su iya yi.
Wannan fim ne mai sauƙi.
Na yi tunani kamar yadda na yi a wasu fina-finan Johnny English: Shin masana'antar fim ta Burtaniya ba za ta iya ba Rowan Atkinson rawar da za ta nuna cewa tana da hazaka ba?
Jam'iyyar Labour ta musanta cewa ta tsara wani shiri na bai wa 'yan Birtaniya damar yin aiki na kwanaki hudu amma a biya su albashi na kwanaki biyar
Jam'iyyar Labour ta Jeremy Corbyn za ta yi nazari kan wani tsari mai ban mamaki da zai bai wa 'yan Birtaniya damar yin aiki kwanaki hudu a mako - amma a biya su biyar.
A bayyane yake jam'iyyar tana son shugabannin kamfanoni su ba ma'aikata ƙarin ranar hutu don su amfana daga tanadin da aka samu ta hanyar kera fasaha.
Hakan zai ba ma'aikata damar yin hutu na kwana uku a ƙarshen mako, amma su ci gaba da samun albashi iri ɗaya.
Wasu majiyoyi sun ce wannan ra'ayi ya yi daidai da shirin tattalin arzikin jam'iyyar da kuma shirin da ta yi na ganin an yi amfani da kasar wajen tallafawa ma'aikata.
Ma'aikata sun amince da sauya zuwa mako guda na kwana huɗu don su amfana daga canjin tattalin arziki.
Wani majiya a jam'iyyar Labour ya shaida wa jaridar Sunday Times cewa:  Ana sa ran za a sanar da wani nazari kan manufofin kafin karshen shekara. 
 Ba za a yi wannan ba cikin dare, amma aikin kwana hudu a mako wata manufa ce da ke tafiya tare da tsarin jam'iyyar na daidaita tattalin arzikin ga ma'aikata da kuma dabarun masana'antu gaba daya .
Jam'iyyar Labour ba ita ce ta farko da ta goyi bayan wannan ra'ayin ba, tun da jam'iyyar Green Party ta yi kira ga yin aiki kwana hudu a mako a lokacin yakin neman zaben shekara ta 2017.
Amma a yanzu haka, jam'iyyar Labour ba ta goyi bayan wannan burin ba.
