Mene ne bikin 'yan kasa na duniya kuma shin ya yi wani abu don rage talauci?
A wannan Asabar, birnin New York zai karbi bakuncin bikin Global Citizen, wani biki na kiɗa na shekara-shekara da ke ɗauke da taurari masu ban sha'awa da kuma manufa mai ban sha'awa: kawar da talauci a duniya.
Bikin na Global Citizen, wanda yanzu ya kai shekara bakwai, zai ga dubban mutane suna zuwa babban filin shakatawa na Central Park don ba kawai jin daɗin wasan kwaikwayon daga masu fasaha kamar Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shawn Mendes ba, amma kuma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin manufar bikin, wato kawo ƙarshen talauci ta 2030.
Bikin na Global Citizen, wanda aka fara gudanarwa a shekarar 2012, wani ci gaba ne na Global Poverty Project, wata kungiya mai kare hakkin bil adama ta duniya da ke fatan kawar da talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke yaki da talauci.
Don samun tikiti kyauta zuwa taron (sai dai idan kuna son biyan tikiti na VIP), masu kallo dole ne su cika jerin ayyuka, ko ayyuka, kamar aikin sa kai, aika imel zuwa ga shugaban duniya, kira ta waya ko yin wani ƙoƙari mai amfani don wayar da kan jama'a game da yaƙi da talauci.
Amma har zuwa wane lokaci ne kungiyar Global Citizen za ta iya cimma burinta a cikin shekaru 12 da suka rage?
Shin ra'ayin bayar da kyauta ga mutane da kide kide da wake-wake na kyauta yana shawo kan su su bukaci kira zuwa aiki, ko kuwa wani misali ne na  clicktivism  - yanayin da mutane ke tunanin gaske suna kawo canji ta hanyar sanya hannu kan takarda ko aika tweet?
Tun daga shekarar 2011, Global Citizen ta samu sama da  miliyan 19  na hannun jari  daga magoya bayanta, wadanda ke ba da shawara ga dalilai daban-daban.
A cewar kungiyar, wadannan ayyuka sun taimaka wajen sa shugabannin duniya su dauki alkawura da kuma aiwatar da manufofi da suka kai dala biliyan 37 da ake sa ran za su sauya rayuwar mutane sama da biliyan 2.25 nan da shekarar 2030.
A farkon 2018, ƙungiyar ta ambata alkawura 390 da sanarwar da ta samo asali daga ayyukanta, wanda aƙalla an riga an biya ko an ɗaga wani ɓangare na dala biliyan 10.
Kungiyar ta kiyasta cewa kudaden da aka bayar sun shafi kusan mutane miliyan 649 a duniya.
Babban alkawarin da aka yi shi ne The Power of Nutrition, wata kungiya ta Birtaniya ta masu zuba jari da masu gudanar da ayyukan da suka yi alkawarin  taimaka wa yara su bunkasa damar su , tare da yin alkawarin ba Rwanda fam miliyan 35 don kawo karshen rashin abinci mai gina jiki a kasar bayan da ta karbi sakonni sama da 4,700 daga Global Citizens.
 Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu bayar da tallafi, gwamnatocin kasa da 'yan kasa na duniya kamar ku, za mu iya sanya rashin adalci na rashin abinci mai gina jiki a matsayin bayanin kula na ƙasa a tarihi, "in ji Tracey Ullman, jakadan shirin The Power of Nutrition, ga taron a wani biki da aka gudanar a Landan a watan Afrilu 2018.
Kungiyar ta kuma ce bayan an dauki mataki sama da 5,000 domin neman karin abinci mai gina jiki ga uwaye da yara a Birtaniya, gwamnati ta sanar da bada tallafi ga wani shiri mai suna The Power of Nutrition, wanda zai amfana da mata da yara miliyan 5 ta hanyar bada agajin abinci mai gina jiki.
A cikin amsar daya daga cikin tambayoyin da aka fi yi a shafinsa na yanar gizo,  me ya sa kake ganin cewa zai yiwu a kawo karshen talauci? ,
Global Citizen ta ce:  Hanyar zuwa wannan zai kasance mai tsawo da wahala, a wasu lokatai za mu faɗi kuma mu kasa.
Amma kamar manyan ƙungiyoyin kare haƙƙin ɗan ƙasa da na anti-apartheid da suka riga mu, za mu yi nasara domin muna da ƙarfi tare.
Janet Jackson, The Weeknd, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B, Janelle Monáe na cikin masu zane-zane da za su yi a New York a wannan shekara, inda Deborra-Lee Furness da Hugh Jackman za su jagoranci wasan kwaikwayon.
Amurka na iya amfani da sojan ruwa wajen kafa  toshe  don hana fitar da makamashin Rasha - Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida
Don hana makamashi na Rasha shiga kasuwannin ciki har da Gabas ta Tsakiya, Washington na iya  idan ya cancanta  amfani da Sojojin Ruwa na Amurka, in ji Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka Ryan Zinke, kamar yadda Washington Examiner ta ruwaito.
Zinke ya ce kasancewar Rasha a Syria - musamman inda take aiki a bisa bukatar gwamnatin da ta dace - wata hujja ce da ke ba ta damar gano sabbin kasuwannin makamashi.
 Ina ganin suna Gabas ta Tsakiya ne domin su yi ciniki da makamashi kamar yadda suke yi a Gabashin Turai, cibiyar kudancin Turai , in ji shi.
Amma, jami'in ya ce akwai hanyoyin da za a magance matsalar.
 Amurka za ta iya, tare da Sojojin Ruwa, tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin ruwa sun bude kuma idan ya cancanta, toshe su don tabbatar da cewa ba a sayar da makamashin su ba , in ji shi.
Zinke yana jawabi ne ga masu halartar taron da kungiyar Consumer Energy Alliance ta shirya, wata kungiya mai zaman kanta da ke bayyana kanta a matsayin 'mai magana da yawun masu amfani da makamashi a Amurka.
Ya kwatanta yadda Washington ke hulɗa da Rasha da Iran, ya kuma ce sun yi kama.
 Game da Iran da Rasha, zaɓin tattalin arziki ya fi yawa a cikinƙwarewa da maye gurbin man fetur, in ji shi, yayin da yake magana game da Rasha yana cewa tana da  fiye da igiya a cikin baka  tare da tattalin arzikin da ke dogara da burbushin mai.
Wannan ya zo ne a daidai lokacin da gwamnatin Trump ta yi alkawarin bunkasa fitar da iskar gas zuwa Turai, ta hanyar maye gurbin Rasha, wanda ya fi rahusa ga masu amfani da ita a Turai.
Don yin hakan, wakilan gwamnatin Trump, ciki har da shugaban Amurka Donald Trump da kansa, suna kokarin shawo kan Jamus ta janye daga aikin bututun mai na Nord Stream 2 wanda Trump ya ce yana sa birnin Berlin ya zama fursuna ga Moscow.
Moscow ta sha nanata cewa bututun mai mai mai da darajar dala biliyan 11, wanda ake sa ran zai ninka na yanzu zuwa mita biliyan 110, aikin tattalin arziki ne kawai.
Kremlin ta ce Washington ta nuna adawa da wannan shiri ne saboda dalilai na tattalin arziki kuma misali ne na gasa mara kyau.
A wata jawabi da ya yi a watan Satumba a Moscow bayan ganawa da sakataren samar da makamashi na Amurka Rick Perry, ministan samar da makamashi na Rasha Alexander Novak ya ce: "Na yi imanin cewa mun yarda cewa ba za a iya amfani da makamashi a matsayin kayan aiki ba kuma masu amfani da makamashi su zabi masu samar da su".
Matsayin Amurka ya jawo mummunan martani daga Jamus, wadda ta sake tabbatar da cewa tana da hannu a wannan aikin.
Babban kungiyar masana'antu ta Jamus, BDI, ta yi kira ga Amurka da ta guji shiga cikin manufofin makamashi na Turai da kuma yarjejeniyar da Berlin da Moscow suka kulla.
 Ina da babbar matsala idan wata ƙasa ta uku ta tsoma baki a cikin samar da makamashi , in ji Dieter Kempf, darektan ƙungiyar masana'antun Jamus (BDI) bayan ganawar da aka yi kwanan nan tsakanin shugabar gwamnatin Jamus Angela Merkel da shugaban Rasha Vladimir Putin.
Elizabeth Warren za ta yi la'akari da yiwuwar tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa a 2020, in ji Sanata daga Massachusetts
Sanata daga Massachusetts Elizabeth Warren ta sanar a ranar Asabar cewa za ta yi la'akari da yiwuwar tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben tsakiyar shekara.
A wani taron jama'a a Holyoke, Massachusetts, Warren ta tabbatar da cewa za ta yi tunanin tsayawa takara.
 Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington su gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace, kuma don hakan, dole ne mace ta kasance a saman , in ji ta, a cewar The Hill.
 Bayan ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zan yi la'akari da takarar shugaban kasa. 
Warren ta bayyana yadda take ji game da Shugaba Donald Trump a taron jama'a, tana mai cewa yana jagorantar kasar nan zuwa hanya mara kyau.
 Na damu matuka da abin da Donald Trump ke yi wa dimokradiyyarmu , in ji ta.
Warren ta fito fili ta soki Trump da kuma dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh.
A ranar Juma'a, Warren ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa: "A bayyane yake muna bukatar binciken FBI kafin mu kada kuri'a".
Sai dai kuma wani binciken da aka fitar a ranar Alhamis ya nuna cewa yawancin masu zaben Warren ba su yarda cewa ya kamata ta tsaya takara a 2020.
A cewar wani bincike da Cibiyar Binciken Siyasa ta Jami'ar Suffolk da kuma jaridar Boston Globe suka yi, kashi 58 cikin 100 na masu jefa kuri'a a Massachusetts sun ce bai kamata 'yar majalisar dattijai ta yi takara ba.
Kashi 32 cikin ɗari sun amince da wannan kamfen.
Binciken ya nuna cewa tsohon gwamna Deval Patrick ya fi samun goyon baya, inda kashi 38 cikin 100 ke goyon bayan kamfen da ake son yi, kashi 48 cikin 100 kuma suna adawa da shi.
Sauran manyan sunayen 'yan jam'iyyar Democrat da aka ambata a cikin kamfen na 2020 sun hada da tsohon mataimakin shugaban kasa Joe Biden da Sanata Bernie Sanders na Vermont.
A cewar Associated Press, Biden ya ce zai yanke shawara a hukumance a watan Janairu.
Sarah Palin ta yi magana game da PTSD na Track Palin a lokacin taron Donald Trump
