A ranar Litinin da yamma aka kama shi kuma aka tuhume shi da aikata wani mummunan aiki a gida.
 Abin da ɗana yake ji a yanzu, abin da yake ji a lokacin da ya dawo gida, zan iya danganta shi da sauran iyalai da ke fama da sakamakon PTSD da wasu raunukan da sojojinmu ke dawowa da su  ta fada wa masu sauraro a taron Donald Trump a Tulsa, Oklahoma.
Palin ta kira kama ta  batun da ba a saba da shi  kuma ta ce game da ɗanta da sauran tsoffin sojoji sun dawo da ɗan bambanci, sun taurare, suna tambayar kansu ko ana girmama abin da abokansu da membobin rundunar sojan sama, da kowane soja, suka ba ƙasar .
Dan Bennett, mai magana da yawun rundunar 'yan sanda ta Wasilla, ya ce an kama shi a ranar Litinin a Wasilla, Alaska, kuma an tuhume shi da cin zarafi da kuma cin zarafin mace a cikin gida, wanda ya shafi rahoton cin zarafin mata da kuma mallakar makami a cikin maye.
Jihohi 18 da Gundumar Columbia sun goyi bayan ƙalubalanci sabuwar manufar neman mafaka
Jihohi 18 da gundumar Columbia sun goyi bayan ƙalubalanci doka game da sabuwar manufar Amurka da ke hana waɗanda suka tsere daga ƙungiyoyin 'yan daba ko kuma waɗanda ke fama da zalunci a gida mafaka.
A ranar Juma'a a Washington, wakilan jihohi 18 da gundumar sun gabatar da wata takarda a madadin wani mai neman mafaka da ya yi hamayya da wannan manufar, in ji NBC News.
Ba a bayyana cikakken sunan mai shigar da kara a shari'ar Grace v. Sessions da kungiyar kare hakkin bil adama ta Amurka ta gabatar a watan Agusta ba.
Ta ce abokin aikinta da 'ya'yanta maza, 'yan kungiyar' yan bindiga, sun yi mata fyade, amma hukumomin Amurka sun yanke shawarar kin amincewa da bukatar da ta yi ta neman mafaka a ranar 20 ga watan Yuli.
An tsare ta a Texas.
Masu gabatar da kara daga jihohin da ke goyon bayan Grace sun bayyana El Salvador, Honduras da Guatemala, waɗanda ke haifar da yawan buƙatun mafaka a Amurka, a matsayin ƙasashe da ke fuskantar matsalolin ƙungiyoyi da tashin hankali na gida.
Sabuwar manufar neman mafaka ta Amurka ta soke hukuncin da Hukumar Kula da 'Yan Gudun Hijira ta yanke a shekarar 2014 wanda ya ba da damar masu shiga cikin gida ba bisa ka'ida ba da ke tserewa daga tashin hankali na gida su nemi mafaka.
Karl Racine, babban lauyan gundumar Columbia, ya bayyana a wata sanarwa a ranar Juma'a cewa sabuwar manufar  ta yi watsi da shekarun da suka gabata na dokokin jihohi, tarayya da na duniya .
 Dokar tarayya ta ce duk bukatar neman mafaka dole ne a bincika ta bisa ga takamaiman gaskiya da yanayin da ake nema, kuma irin wannan haramcin ya sabawa wannan ƙa'idar , in ji amicus curiae a cikin takardar shaidarsa.
Lauyoyin sun kuma yi jayayya a cikin takardar cewa hana baƙi shiga ƙasar na cutar da tattalin arzikin Amurka, suna cewa suna iya zama 'yan kasuwa da kuma samar da aikin da ake buƙata.
Babban mai gabatar da kara Jeff Sessions ya umurci alƙalan shige da fice a watan Yuni da su daina ba da mafaka ga waɗanda ke tserewa daga tashin hankali a cikin gida da kuma ƙungiyoyin 'yan daba.
 Ana ba da mafaka ga mutanen da suka bar ƙasarsu saboda tsanantawa ko tsoro saboda launin fata, imani, ƙasa, ƙungiyar zamantakewa ko ra'ayin siyasa,  Sessions ya ce a ranar 11 ga Yuni, a sanarwar da ya yi game da wannan manufar.
 Ba a taɓa tsara mafaka don magance dukan matsalolin da mutane suke fuskanta a kowace rana a faɗin duniya ba. 
An yi ta kokarin ceto mutane a Palu yayin da adadin wadanda suka mutu ya ninka a kokarin neman wadanda suka tsira
Amma, waɗanda suka tsira sun ƙara baƙin ciki.
 Ina jin matukar damuwa , in ji Risa Kusuma, wata mahaifiya mai shekaru 35, tana ta'azantar da ɗanta da ke fama da zazzabi a Palu, cibiyar kwashe mutane daga garin da aka yi watsi da shi.
 A kowane lokaci, ana kawo gawawwaki a cikin motar asibiti.
Ba a samun ruwa mai tsabta a wurare da yawa.
An ga mazauna garin suna komawa gidajen da aka lalata, suna tara kayan da suka yi ruwa a ciki, suna ƙoƙarin ceto duk abin da suka samu.
Daruruwan mutane sun ji rauni kuma asibitocin da girgizar kasar mai karfin maki 7.5 ta lalata sun cika da ruwa.
Wasu daga cikin wadanda suka ji rauni, ciki har da Dwi Haris, wanda ya karye a baya da kafadu, sun huta a gaban asibitin soji na Palu, inda ake kula da marasa lafiya a waje saboda mummunan rauni.
Ya yi kuka sosai sa'ad da ya gaya mana yadda girgizar ƙasar ta girgiza ɗakin da yake zama a ciki da matarsa da 'yarsa.
Ba mu sami lokacin da za mu ceci kanmu ba.
