Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da  tsoratarwa  ta hanyar  tallan farfaganda 
Mako guda bayan da wata jaridar kasar Sin ta buga wata talla mai shafi hudu a wata jaridar Amurka da ke nuna amfanin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da amfani da jaridar Amurka wajen yada farfaganda.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi magana a ranar Laraba game da ƙarin kuɗin da China Daily ta biya a cikin jaridar Des Moines Register - jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a Iowa  bayan da ya zargi China da ƙoƙarin tsoma baki a zaɓen majalisar dokokin Amurka na 6 ga Nuwamba, zargin da China ta musanta.
A lokacin da ya zargi Beijing da kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka, Trump ya nuna abin da jami'an Amurka suka shaida wa Reuters cewa wani sabon mataki ne a cikin yakin da Washington ke yi na matsa lamba kan China.
A yayin da gwamnatocin kasashen waje ke amfani da tallace-tallace don bunkasa kasuwanci, Beijing da Washington a yanzu suna cikin yakin kasuwanci da ke kara tsanantawa wanda ya sa su sanya haraji kan kayayyakin da suke shigowa da su.
A farkon yakin cinikayya, matakan da China ta dauka na haraji an yi su ne don a yi wa masu fitar da kayayyaki daga jihohi kamar Iowa da ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Trump ta Republican, in ji masana na kasar Sin da Amurka.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma tsohon gwamnan Iowa, babban mai fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa China, ya ce Beijing ta cutar da ma'aikatan Amurka, manoma da kamfanoni.
China, Branstad ya rubuta a wata kasida a jaridar Des Moines Register a ranar Lahadi,  tana kara tsoratar da mu ta hanyar yada farfaganda a cikin jaridarmu ta kyauta .
 A cikin yada farfagandar da take yi, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi amfani da al'adun Amurka na 'yancin faɗar albarkacin baki da' yancin 'yan jarida ta hanyar saka tallace-tallace da aka biya a jaridar Des Moines Register, Branstad ya rubuta.
 A gefe guda, a ofishin jarida na Beijing, ba za ka ga muryoyin adawa da yawa ba kuma ba za ka ga ainihin ra'ayoyin da ya bambanta da Sinawa ke da shi game da yanayin tattalin arzikin kasar Sin ba, saboda kafofin watsa labarai suna bin jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin, in ji shi.
Ya kara da cewa wani daga cikin manyan jaridu a kasar Sin ya kauce wa buga  labarinsa, amma bai bayyana jaridar ba.
Masu bincike sun yi gargadin cewa 'yan Republican na janye masu jefa kuri'a a lokacin da za a gudanar da zaben tsakiyar shekara saboda rashin nasarar Kavanaugh
Yayin da manyan 'yan Republican da dama ke kare Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka nada a kotun koli a bayan zargin cin zarafin mata, manazarta sun yi gargadin cewa za a iya samun mummunan sakamako, musamman tsakanin mata a zaben tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa.
A halin yanzu, akwai damuwa sosai game da wannan batu, kuma yawancin 'yan Republican sun riga sun nuna a fili cewa suna son a yi zaben.
A wata kasida da aka buga a ranar 29 ga watan Satumba a jaridar The Hill, Grant Reeher, farfesa a fannin kimiyyar siyasa a makarantar Maxwell a jami'ar Syracuse ya ce ba za a iya komawa baya ba.
Reeher ya kara da cewa yana shakkar cewa kokarin da Sanata Jeff Flake (R-Ariz.) ya yi a minti na karshe don neman binciken FBI zai isa ya kwantar da fushin masu jefa kuri'a.
Karine Jean-Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara kuma mai magana da yawun kungiyar MoveOn ta kasar, ta ce, "Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba; ba za su manta da gobe ba, ba a watan Nuwamba ba", in ji ta a ranar 28 ga Satumba, a cewar jaridar Washington.
A safiyar ranar Juma'a, Mic ta ruwaito, masu zanga-zangar sun yi ihu  Nuwamba ta zo!  a cikin zauren majalisar dattijai yayin da 'yan Republican da ke kula da kwamitin shari'a suka zabi su ci gaba da nadin Kavanaugh duk da shaidar da Dokta Christine Blasey Ford ta bayar.
 Ƙwarin gwiwa da kuma motsawar dimokiradiyya za su wuce kima , in ji Stu Rothenberg, mai nazarin siyasa.
Mutane suna cewa ya riga ya yi yawa.
Amma wannan zai iya zama mafi girma, musamman a tsakanin mata masu jefa kuri'a a unguwannin da ke kusa da unguwar da kuma matasa masu shekaru 18 zuwa 29 waɗanda ko da yake ba sa son shugaban kasa, ba sa yawan yin zabe. 
Tun kafin a fara gabatar da shaidar Ford a gaban jama'a, inda ya bayyana dalla-dalla zargin cin zarafin da ake yi wa wanda aka zaba a kotun koli, manazarta sun yi hasashen cewa za a yi tawaye idan 'yan Republican suka tabbatar da hakan.
A cewar NBC News, tsohon shugaban kwamitin jam'iyyar Republican, Michael Steele, ya ce a farkon makon da ya gabata cewa  Wannan ya zama rikici ga GOP .
 Ba wai kawai batun zaben kwamitin ba ne ko kuma na karshe, ko kuma na nadin Kavanaugh. Har ila yau, batun yadda 'yan Republican suka gudanar da lamarin da kuma yadda suka magance shi ne , Guy Cecil, darektan United States Priorities, wata ƙungiya da ke taimaka wa 'yan Democrat da aka zaɓa, ya lura a cikin wani labarin talabijin.
Amma bayan shaidar Ford da Kavanaugh, jama'ar Amirka sun rabu biyu game da amincin bangarorin biyu, kuma kaɗan ne kawai suka goyi bayan bangaren biyu.
Wani sabon binciken da YouGov ya yi ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin ɗari na waɗanda aka yi wa bincike sun gaskata ko kuma sun yi imani da shaidar Ford, yayin da kashi 35 cikin ɗari suka ce sun gaskata ko kuma sun yi imani da Kavanaugh.
Bugu da ƙari, kashi 38 cikin ɗari sun ce sun gaskata cewa Kavanaugh ya yi ƙarya ko kuma ya yi ƙarya a lokacin da yake ba da shaida, yayin da kashi 30 cikin ɗari ne kawai suka ce hakan game da Ford.
A cewar jaridar The Guardian, hukumar ta FBI na binciken zargin da Ford da akalla wata mai gabatar da kara, Deborah Ramirez suka yi bayan da Sanata Flake ya matsa mata.
Ford ta shaida a gaban kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattijai a makon da ya gabata cewa Kavanaugh ya yi mata fyade a lokacin da take da shekaru 17 da haihuwa.
Ramirez ya ce a lokacin da suke Yale a shekarun 1980s, wanda ke neman zama a Kotun Koli ya nuna mata al'aurarsa a wani biki.
Wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo ya shirya sabuwar intanet da za ta kalubalanci Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo, ya kaddamar da wani sabon kamfani da ke neman yin gasa da Facebook, Amazon da Google.
Aikin da ya fi kwanan nan na almara na fasaha, Inrupt, kamfani ne da ke amfani da dandamali na kyauta na Berners-Lee Solid.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda aka adana bayanan su da kuma waɗanda aka ba da izinin samun damar wannan ko wannan bayanin.
A wata hira da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi dariya cewa Inrupt na da burin  mamaye duniya .
Ya ce, "Ya kamata mu yi hakan yanzu".
Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi.
Aikace-aikacen yana amfani da fasahar Solid don bawa mutane damar ƙirƙirar nasu kantin sayar da bayanan sirri na kan layi ko DPL.
Wannan zai iya ɗauke da jerin sunayen abokan aiki, jerin abubuwan da za a yi, kalanda, laburaren waƙa da kuma wasu kayan aiki na kai da na sana'a.
Kamar dai Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack da Spotify duk suna aiki a lokaci guda a cikin mai bincike guda.
Wani abu na musamman game da kantin sayar da bayanan sirri na kan layi shine cewa mai amfani ne ke yanke shawarar wanda zai iya samun damar irin bayanan.
Kamfanoni suna kiran wannan "hakkin mutum ta hanyar bayanai".
A cewar shugaban kamfanin, John Bruce, manufar Inrupt ita ce kamfanin ya samar da albarkatu, matakai da ƙwarewa don sa kowa ya sami damar amfani da Solid.
A halin yanzu, kamfanin ya ƙunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro da IBM ta saya, wasu masu haɓaka da ke aiki a kan kwangila a kan aikin da kuma ƙungiyar masu aikin sa kai.
Daga wannan makon, masu haɓaka fasaha a duk faɗin duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen da aka rarraba ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke kan gidan yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba su tattauna da Facebook da Google ba game da ko za su yi wani canji na gaba daya inda duk tsarin kasuwancin su zai rushe gaba daya a wani lokaci.
Ba ma neman izini daga wurin su.
A wata kasida da aka buga a ranar Asabar a kan Medium, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa aikin [Inrupt] shine samar da wutar lantarki da tsarin halittu don kare mutuncin da ingancin sabon yanar gizo wanda aka gina akan Solid.
A shekara ta 1994, a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts, Berners-Lee ya kawo canji a Intanet ta hanyar kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya.
A cikin 'yan watannin da suka gabata, Berners-Lee ya kasance mai tasiri a muhawara game da tsaka tsaki na cibiyar sadarwa.
Ko da yake ya kafa Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai kasance mai kafa da kuma darektan Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya, Gidauniyar Yanar Gizo da Cibiyar Bayanai ta Open.
 Ina da kwarin gwiwa game da sabuwar zamanin yanar gizo , Berners-Lee ya kara da cewa.
Bernard Vann: An yi bikin girmama wani limamin da ya yi yaƙi a Yaƙin Duniya na Ɗaya
Limamin cocin Ingila da ya samu lambar yabo ta Victoria Cross a lokacin Yaƙin Duniya na Ɗaya a matsayin ɗan gwagwarmaya an yi bikin tunawa da shi a garinsu shekaru 100 bayan haka.
Lt. Colonel Bernard Vann ya sami wannan lambar yabo a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, a lokacin da aka kai hari a Bellenglise da Lehaucourt.
Amma, bayan kwana huɗu, wani ɗan bindiga ya kashe shi, kuma bai san cewa an ba shi lambar yabo mafi girma a ƙasar Britaniya ba.
'Ya'yanta biyu sun buɗe wani dutse a wani bikin tunawa da ita a birnin Rushden, da ke Northamptonshire a ranar Asabar da ta gabata.
Ɗansa Michael Vann, ya ce wannan abin da aka bayyana a kan dutse daidai shekaru 100 bayan nasarar da kakansa ya yi, yana da alama sosai.
A cewar London Gazette, a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 1918, Laftanar Kanar Vann ya jagoranci rukuninsa a kan tashar St. Quentin  ta cikin hazo mai yawa da kuma wuta mai tsanani daga bindigogi da bindigogi .
Daga baya ya ruga zuwa layin harbi kuma, tare da  babban ƙarfin hali , ya jagoranci layin kafin ya busa wani bindiga na ƙasar da kansa kuma ya kashe sojoji uku na rukunin.
A ranar 4 ga Oktoba, 1918, wani ɗan Jamus mai harbi ya kashe Lt. Col. Vann, wata ɗaya kafin ƙarshen yaƙin.
Michael Vann, ɗan shekara 72, ya ce ayyukan kakansa  abu ne da ba zan taɓa cim ma ba, amma hakan ya sa na ƙasƙantar da kaina .
Shi da ɗan'uwansa, Dr. James Vann, sun kuma saka kambi bayan bikin da ƙungiyar matasa ta Brentwood Imperial suka gudanar.
Michael Vann ya ce yana jin  babban gata ne ya kasance cikin wannan zanga-zangar  kuma ya kara da cewa  ƙarfin hali na jarumi na gaske yana nunawa a cikin goyon bayan da mutane da yawa zasu ba shi .
