Da karfe 6 na safe, yayin da Gegard Mousasi da Rory MacDonald ke shirin fafatawa, masu kallo a Burtaniya sun yi mamaki lokacin da aka canza watsa shirye-shiryen zuwa Peppa Pig.
Wasu sun yi fushi cewa sun yi barci har safiya don su yi yaƙi.
