Mickelson ya yi rashin lafiya a gasar Ryder Cup a ranar Asabar
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson zai buga wasan Ryder Cup karo na 47 a ranar Lahadi, amma zai bukaci gyarawa don kauce wa wannan mummunan mataki.
Mickelson, wanda ya shiga gasar shekara biyu a karo na 12, ya yi nasara a gasar, amma sai da kyaftin Jim Furyk ya kore shi daga wasan kwallon kafa na ranar Asabar.
Maimakon ya kasance a tsakiyar wasan kamar yadda ya saba yi a Amurka, zakaran ya raba ranarsa tsakanin zama mai goyon baya da kuma gyara wasan da yake yi a filin wasa don magance matsalolinsa.
Bai taɓa zama babban jagora ba, ko da a lokacin da ya fi ƙwarewa a aikinsa, kuma a shekara 48, ba shi da kyau a gasar Golf National, inda tsayi mai tsawo ke hukunta kuskuren da aka yi.
Kuma kamar dai wannan wasan ba shi da ban tsoro, Mickelson a wasa na tara a ranar Lahadi ya fafata da Francesco Molinari, wanda ya lashe gasar Open ta Birtaniya, wanda ya yi aiki tare da Tommy Fleetwood a wannan makon don lashe wasanninsu hudu.
Idan Amurkawa, da suka ci hudu a wasan farko na wasanni 12 na wasan kwaikwayo, suka fara da kyau, wasan Mickelson zai iya zama mai mahimmanci.
Furyk ya nuna cewa ya amince da mutumin, amma ba zai iya faɗa wani abu ba.
Furyk ya ce, "Ya fahimci rawar da yake takawa a yau, ya bugo ni baya, ya rungume ni kuma ya ce zai kasance a shirye gobe".
 Yana da gaba gaɗi sosai.
Shi gwarzo ne kuma ya ƙara abubuwa da yawa ga waɗannan ƙungiyoyi a baya, kamar wannan makon.
Wataƙila ban taɓa ganin shi yana wasa biyu ba.
Na yi tunanin cewa ba haka ba ne, amma wannan shi ne yadda ya faru kuma wannan shi ne yadda muka ji cewa ya kamata mu yi.
Yana son ya je wurin kamar yadda kowa yake so.
A ranar Lahadi, Mickelson zai doke Nick Faldo a kan yawan wasannin Ryder Cup da aka buga.
Wannan zai iya nuna ƙarshen aikinsa a gasar Ryder Cup wanda bai taɓa kaiwa matsayin da ya kafa ba.
Mickelson ya ci 18, ya yi rashin nasara 20, kuma ya ci wasanni bakwai, ko da yake Furyk ya ce kasancewarsa ya kawo abubuwa masu mahimmanci ga tawagar.
Yana da ban dariya, mai ba'a, mai hankali, yana son yin ba'a da mutane, kuma babban mutum ne da za a samu a cikin ɗakin wasan, in ji shi.
 Ina ganin 'yan wasan da suka fi ƙarami sun ji daɗin yin gasa da shi a wannan makon, kuma hakan ya sa ni farin ciki sosai.
