Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta addabi birnin Palu na Indonesia a ranar Juma'a suka kashe, in ji hukumomi, kuma ana sa ran adadin zai karu.
A sakamakon katsewar sadarwa, jami'an agaji ba su samu wani bayani daga yankin Donggala da ke arewacin birnin Palu ba, wanda ya fi kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasar mai karfin awo 7.5.
A birnin Palu, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga wurin da bala'in ya auku.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palu da Donggala a Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi ne, wanda ke kan iyakar wani kunkuntar bakin teku a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, wanda yawan jama'arsa ya kai 379,800 a shekarar 2017.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasar da tsunami suka auku, birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafa shi.
Donggala wani yanki ne da ke da nisan kilomita 300 (180 miles) na gabar teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
An kiyasta yawan mazaunan yankin, yanki ne na gudanarwa a ƙarƙashin lardi, a cikin 299,200 a cikin 2017.
Kifi da noma sune manyan ginshiƙan tattalin arzikin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman yankin Donggala da ke gabar teku.
Har ila yau, hakar ma'adinai na nickel yana da muhimmanci a lardin, amma an fi samunsa a Morowali, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
Palu da Donggala sun sha fama da tsunami sau da yawa a cikin karni guda, a cewar Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, guguwar tsunami da aka yi a garin Donggala ta kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ta halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje.
A shekara ta 1996, wata guguwar tsunami ta addabi yammacin Donggala kuma ta kashe mutane tara.
Ƙasar Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake yawan girgizar ƙasa a cikin tekun Fasifik kuma ana yawan girgizar ƙasa a wurin.
Ga wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami na 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, wata babbar girgizar ƙasa da ta auku a yammacin lardin Aceh a ƙasar Indonesia ta haddasa tsunami da ya shafi ƙasashe 14, kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabi cikinsu a birnin Aceh.
2005: Ƙarƙashin tekun yammacin Sumatra ya yi girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi daga ƙarshen Maris zuwa farkon Afrilu.
Wasu mutane ɗarurruwa sun mutu a tsibirin Nias da ke bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta auku a kudancin Java, tsibirin da ke da yawan jama'a a ƙasar Indonesia, kuma hakan ya jawo tsunami da ya auku a kudancin tsibirin kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 700.
2009: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 ta afkawa birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta halaka tsibirin Mentawai da ke bakin tekun Sumatra kuma ta haddasa tsunami mai tsawon mita 10 da ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wata girgizar kasa ta girgiza yankin Pidie Jaya da ke Aceh, ta haddasa barna da firgici, ta tunatar da mazauna yankin da bala'in girgizar kasa da tsunami na shekarar 2004 suka yi.
Babu wata tsunami da ta faru a wannan karon, amma mutane sama da 100 sun mutu sakamakon rushewar gine-gine.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi ta girgiza tsibirin yawon buɗe ido na Lombok na Indonesia, ta kashe mutane sama da 500, galibi a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata gine-gine dubbai kuma ta bar dubban masu yawon buɗe ido a makale na ɗan lokaci.
