Track Palin, babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska kuma dan takarar mataimakin shugaban kasa Sarah Palin, an kama shi da laifin hari.
An kama Palin, mai shekara 29, daga Wasilla, Alaska, bisa zargin cin zarafin mata, sabawa rahoton cin zarafin mata da kuma tsayayya da kama, a cewar wata sanarwa da 'yan sandan jihar Alaska suka fitar a ranar Asabar.
Rahoton 'yan sanda ya ce ya karɓi wayar wata mace da ya sani da ke ƙoƙarin kiran 'yan sanda don kai rahoton laifin da ake zargi.
