An ce waɗannan zargin biyu za su iya jawo hukuncin kisa.
Makonni bayan wannan hari, wata babbar kotun tarayya ta yanke wa Saipov hukuncin kisa a kan wasu laifuka 22, ciki har da laifuka takwas na kisan kai da kuma karkatar da kudade, wanda yawanci masu gabatar da kara ke amfani da su a shari'o'in aikata laifuka da kuma daya don aikata laifuka na tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Masu gabatar da kara sun ce harin ya bukaci  shiri sosai da kuma shiri , inda suka bayyana yadda Saipov ya yi amfani da shi a matsayin mummunar hanya, ta zalunci da lalata .
 Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi wa dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco rauni, lalacewa da asarar rayukansu , in ji sanarwar.
Biyar cikin waɗanda aka kashe 'yan yawon buɗe ido ne daga ƙasar Ajantina.
