An samu wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, da laifin kashe wasu 'yan dillalan miyagun kwayoyi biyu amma daga bisani aka yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a watan Satumbar 2009.
A shekara ta 1953 ne aka yi hukuncin kisa a New York a kan Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka kashe don yin tawaye da leƙen asiri ga Tarayyar Soviet a cikin shekaru biyu bayan Yaƙin Cacar Baki.
An kashe Rosenberg biyu ta wurin kujerar lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
