Warren ya yi niyyar yin la'akari da yiwuwar tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa
A ranar Asabar, Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta ce za ta yi la'akari da yiwuwar tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Jaridar Boston Globe ta ruwaito cewa, 'yar jam'iyyar Democrat daga Massachusetts ta tattauna game da makomar ta a ranar Asabar a wani taron jama'a a yammacin Massachusetts.
Warren, wanda ya kasance mai sukar Shugaba Donald Trump, yana neman sake zaɓe a watan Nuwamba da Geoff Diehl, wakilin GOP a jihohi, wanda ya kasance shugaban haɗin gwiwa a 2016 don kamfen ɗin Trump a Massachusetts.
Ta kasance a tsakiyar jita-jita cewa za ta iya fuskantar Trump a 2020.
Taron da aka yi a yammacin Asabar a birnin Holyoke shi ne taro na 36 da ya yi da masu jefa kuri'a a taron jama'a tun lokacin da Trump ya hau mulki.
Wani mai halarta ya tambaye ta ko tana da niyyar tsayawa takarar shugaban kasa.
Warren ta ce lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington don gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace, kuma hakan na nufin cewa mata za su zama shugaban kasa.
