Patrick Dwyer ya ci wa Giants kwallo biyu a wasan da suka yi da Dundee
Dundee Stars sun share rashin nasarar da suka sha a gasar Elite a ranar Juma'a da suka sha a hannun Belfast Giants ta hanyar doke wasan da suka yi a Dundee ranar Asabar da ta gabata.
Giants sun buɗe ci gaban da suka ci biyu daga Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cownie sun ci wasan da aka ci a gida kafin Dwyer ya sake bai wa Giants damar cin nasara.
François Bouchard ya daidaita wa Dundee kafin Lukas Lundvald Nielsen ya ci biyu, ya tabbatar da nasarar.
Wannan dai shi ne karo na uku da 'yan wasan Adam Keefe suka sha kashi a gasar Elite League a bana, inda suka doke Dundee 2-1 a ranar Juma'a da daddare a Belfast, bayan da suka ci gaba da zama a baya.
