Dwyer ya ci gaba da cin kwallo a minti na hudu, 3:35 da Kendall McFaull ya buga, yayin da David Rutherford ya yi amfani da Beauvillier wanda ya sake ninka kwallon bayan minti hudu.
A cikin wani lokaci mai kyau na farko, Sullivan ya sake dawo da 'yan wasan gida a 13:10 kafin Matt Marquardt ya shiga Cownie, a 15:16, tare da daidaitawa.
Dwyer ya tabbatar da cewa Giants sun ci gaba kafin hutun farko lokacin da ya ci kwallo ta biyu a daren a ƙarshen zangon farko.
Sai 'yan wasan gida suka sake haduwa kuma Bouchard ya sake daidaitawa da kwallo daya wanda ya ba da damar lamba a 27:37.
Cownie da Charles Corcoran sun yi aiki tare don taimakawa Nielsen sanya Dundee a gaban wasan a karo na farko a ƙarshen rabi na biyu, don haka ya tabbatar da nasarar tawagarsa ta hanyar zura kwallo ta biyar a tsakiyar.
Giants, da suka yi rashin nasara a wasanni hudu daga cikin biyar da suka buga, za su karbi bakuncin Milton Keynes a wasansu na gaba ranar Juma'a.
