Kamfanin jirgin saman da ya yi hadarin jirgin da ya fada cikin wani tafkin da ke tekun Pacific a Micronesia ya ce yanzu an rasa mutum guda bayan da fasinjoji 47 da ma'aikatan jirgin suka tsere daga jirgin da ke nitsewa.
Air Niugini ta bayyana a wata sanarwa cewa tun daga ranar Asabar da yamma ba ta iya gano wani fasinja namiji ba.
Kamfanin jirgin ya ce yana aiki tare da hukumomin yankin, asibitoci da masu bincike don gano mutumin.
Kamfanin jirgin bai amsa nan da nan ba ga ƙarin bayani game da fasinja, kamar shekarun sa ko ƙasarsa.
Jiragen ruwa na cikin gida sun taimaka wajen ceto sauran fasinjoji da ma'aikatan jirgin bayan jirgin ya yi karo da ruwa yayin da yake kokarin sauka a filin jirgin saman Chuuk Island.
Hukumomi sun ce a ranar Juma'a an kwantar da mutane bakwai a asibiti.
Kamfanin jirgin ya ce a ranar Asabar, fasinjoji shida suna asibiti, kuma dukkansu suna cikin koshin lafiya.
Har yanzu ba a san ainihin dalilin hadarin ba.
Kamfanin jirgin sama na Amurka da kuma rundunar sojin ruwa sun ce jirgin ya sauka a cikin wani tafki kusa da filin saukar jirgin.
Wasu shaidu sun ce jirgin ya tsallake hanyar jirgin.
Wani matukin jirgin Bill Jaynes ya ce jirgin ya sauka ƙasa sosai.
Jaynes ta ce: "Wannan abu ne mai kyau.
Jaynes ya ce shi da sauran sun yi nasarar shiga cikin ruwan har zuwa tashoshin ceto na jirgin da ke nitsewa.
Ya ce ma'aikatan jirgin sun firgita kuma sun yi ihu, kuma ya ji rauni a kansa.
Rundunar Sojojin Ruwa ta Amurka ta ce ma'aikatan jirgin ruwa da ke aiki a kusa da wurin da ake gyara wani tashar jirgin ruwa sun kuma taimaka wajen ceto ta amfani da jirgin ruwa mai iska don kwashe mutane zuwa gabar teku kafin jirgin ya nutse cikin ruwa mai tsawon mita 30.
