A ranar Asabar ne masu gabatar da kara suka dage shari'ar da ake yi wa wani mutum da ake zargi da kona wata mata da rai a Mississippi a 2014.
Wani mai bincike a ma'aikatar shari'a ta Amirka, Paul Rowlett ya yi shaidar sa'o'i da yawa a matsayin masani a fannin bincike na leken asiri.
Ya bayyana wa juri yadda ya yi amfani da bayanan wayar salula don gano inda wanda ake tuhuma mai shekaru 29, Quinton Tellis, da kuma wanda aka kashe mai shekaru 19, Jessica Chambers, suka tafi a daren da aka kashe ta.
Rowlett ya ce ya samu bayanan wurin da aka yi amfani da wayoyin salula da dama da suka nuna cewa Tellis yana tare da Chambers a daren da ya mutu, wanda ya sabawa bayanan da ya yi a baya, The Clarion Ledger ta ruwaito.
