Ƙungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder ta 2018 ta doke ƙungiyar Amurka da ƙimar ƙarshe ta 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a Golf National kusa da Paris, Faransa.
Yanzu haka Amurka ta sha kaye sau shida a jere a Turai kuma ba ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun 1993.
Turai ta sake lashe gasar ne bayan da Thomas Bjorn, kyaftin din Denmark ya ci Amurka da maki 14.5.
Tauraron kwallon kafa na Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya sha wahala a mafi yawan gasar, ya jefa bugun farko a cikin ruwa a rami na 16 a par 3, ya ba da takara ga Francesco Molinari.
Molinari ɗan wasan golf na Italiya ya yi fice a duk zagayensa, ya zama ɗaya daga cikin 'yan wasa huɗu da suka taɓa kaiwa 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a shekarar 1979.
An kori Jordan Spieth na Amurka 5-4 daga wasan da ya fi kowacce kasa a gasar Turai, Thorbjorn Olesen na Denmark.
Dan wasan golf mafi kyau a duniya, Dustin Johnson, ya sha kashi 2 da 1 a hannun Ian Poulter na Ingila, wanda zai iya zama wasan Ryder Cup na karshe.
Wani ɗan wasa da ya lashe gasar Ryder Cup sau takwas, Sergio Garcia ɗan Spain ya zama zakaran Turai na kowane lokaci tare da jimlar maki 25.5.
